                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d01"><locus target="#155v"/><desc><ref type="authFile" corresp="AT1082Angel"/> with <term key="sword"/> and scabbard. Caption in pencil next to wing: <q>“Saint Michael. . .[illegible]”</q>  Caption on <locus target="#156r"/> is the likely original caption: “Who is this? Saint Michael</desc></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d02"><locus target="#156r"/><desc><ref type="authFile" corresp="AT1005Crucifixion"/>,Crude drawing in pencil of Jesus on the Cross</desc></decoNote>
